\f0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cb3 A Social Media Application API Design is a comprehensive blueprint for creating the backend infrastructure that powers a social networking platform. This design outlines the various endpoints and data structures necessary to support core social media functionalities.\AppleTypeServices \'a0
